  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figure. <br /> \rGiven the following information, complete the Last Minute Change (LMC) section of the load sheet and find the LMC TOTAL value. The LMC data:</p>\r\r<div>\r<div>Two male and two female passengers embarked at seat row no. 7.</div>\r\r<div>Four pieces of baggage loaded in cargo compartment no. 5.</div>\r\r<div>A 100-kg cargo box off-loaded from cargo compartment no. 4.</div>\r\r<div>A 50-kg mail box loaded in cargo compartment no. 4.</div>\r\r<div> <br /> \rUse 'all adult' standard masses for passengers and standard masses for baggage for a domestic scheduled flight.</div>\r</div>\r\r<div> </div>",
